_______________________________________________________________________________
"Blindness"   
        Using this power, the psionicist can scramble a target's
        mind in such a way as to prevent the signals from the
        optic nerve from being interpreted.  Effectively, this
        blinds the target.  The duration is based on guild level.
        This ability is PK checked, as with any other attack.
 
SP Cost:  20	Guild Level:  3	  Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  blind <targetname>
